    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法 </h2><br>Bulletrooms 是一款以 Backrooms 宇宙为背景的老式第一人称射击游戏。你需要闯过 Backrooms 的多个关卡，唯一的目标就是生存下来并找到出路。记住，Backrooms 中的所有关卡都居住着危险的实体，但你不必再逃避和躲藏了。现在，你可以反击了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/7d1c11bc455668bd8b98db83791553a7.poster.avif?t=1722180221\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/7d1c11bc455668bd8b98db83791553a7.webm?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/7d1c11bc455668bd8b98db83791553a7.mp4?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器 </h2><br>在 Backrooms 的迷宫中，你可以找到突击步枪、霰弹枪、激光枪、榴弹发射器和火箭发射器。使用所有这些武器，清除密室中的危险实体！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/a136b698f5860a4cb0de9ea3b9794a6d.poster.avif?t=1722180221\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/a136b698f5860a4cb0de9ea3b9794a6d.webm?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/a136b698f5860a4cb0de9ea3b9794a6d.mp4?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关卡 </h2><br>探索现实中不应该存在的走廊和房间。可供您选择的关卡有：The Lobby, Habitable Zone, Pipes, Sublimity, The Windows, The End, Level ! (RUN) 。每个关卡都有独特的危险和攻击性实体在等着你！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/ef88100f9c5f65d47f745d61f2d49281.poster.avif?t=1722180221\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/ef88100f9c5f65d47f745d61f2d49281.webm?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/ef88100f9c5f65d47f745d61f2d49281.mp4?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >实体：</h2><br>您可以选择在密室中出现的生物。这些实体可以是典型的 Backrooms，也可以是下一个机器人，它们看起来各不相同，但你还是可以射杀它们！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/1e007e5e93623fc680a889d39e16cf41.poster.avif?t=1722180221\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/1e007e5e93623fc680a889d39e16cf41.webm?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/1e007e5e93623fc680a889d39e16cf41.mp4?t=1722180221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085730/extras/712f098ee1f08541123deb4e13861b91.avif?t=1722180221\" width=666 height=66 /></span>",
